Type Property# progressMarkUserInfoKey

macOS

```
class let progressMarkUserInfoKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/AppKit/NSAnimation/progressMarkUserInfoKey#Discussion)

Contains the value of an [`NSAnimation.Progress`](/documentation/appkit/nsanimation/progress) as an [`NSNumber`](/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber) instance that indicates the current animation progress. The value will be between `0.0` and `1.0`.
